        AppLanguage.GERMAN -> "Best-effort preservation of ajax pagination / SPA state on back: blocks the page's auto-reload on back navigation and prefers history.back() to hit the page cache. Not guaranteed on all sites; a few sites that refresh data on back may be affected."
        AppLanguage.RUSSIAN -> "Best-effort preservation of ajax pagination / SPA state on back: blocks the page's auto-reload on back navigation and prefers history.back() to hit the page cache. Not guaranteed on all sites; a few sites that refresh data on back may be affected."
